<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<style>
		@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300&display=swap');

		p {
			margin: 0;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		html,
		body {

			background-color: #F5F7FB;
			margin: 0;
		}

		h3,
		h4 {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		div .code {
			font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
			color: #202020;
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 20spx;
		}

		.context {
			font-size: 12px;
			padding: 40px 50px 40px 50px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		.text {
			padding-left: 2rem;
			padding-top: 2rem;
			padding-bottom: 2rem;
			padding-right: 2rem;
			background-color: #FFFFFF;
			font-size: 14px;

		}

		.button {
			background-color: #1FA0DB;
			border: none;
			color: white;
			padding: 15px 32px;
			text-align: center;
			text-decoration: none;
			display: inline-block;
			font-size: 14px;
			margin: 4px 2px;
			cursor: pointer;
		}

		img {
			width: 75%;
			height: 40%;
		}

		.button {
			background-color: #1FA0DB;
			border: none;
			color: white;
			padding: 12px 32px;
			text-decoration: none;
			display: inline-block;
			border-radius: 8px;
			font-size: 12px;
			margin: 4px auto 24px;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: transform .3s;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		.atc_button {
			background-color: #FFFFFF;
			border: none;
			color: #444;
			padding: 8px 24px;
			text-decoration: none;
			display: inline-block;
			border-radius: 8px;
			border: 1px solid #444;
			font-size: 12px;
			margin: 32px auto 24px;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: all .3s;
			font-weight: 500;
		}
		.atc_button .callogo {
			display: inline-block;
			height: 16px;
			vertical-align: middle;
			margin: 0 0 2px 6px;
			color: inherit;
		}

		.button:hover {
			color: #FFFFFF;
			transform: scale(1.1);
		}

		.atc_button:hover {
			color: #FFF;
			background-color: #444;
			transform: scale(1.1);
		}

		.links {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}

		@media(max-width: 600px) {
			.context {
				margin-left: 0;
				margin-right: 0;
			}



			div .code h1 {
				font-size: 1.3rem;

			}
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class='context'>


		<div class="code">
			<img src="{{img}}"></img>
		</div>
		<div class="text">
			Hello {{name}},
			<br>
			<p style="margin-bottom: 16px">
				Greetings from InterviewDeck. We have scheduled an interview for company
				<span style="color: #1FA0DB; font-weight:500">{{company}}</span>.
			</p>
			<div style="display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;flex-direction:column">
				<p>The interview is scheduled from</p>
				<p style="color: #666; font-weight: 500;margin-bottom: 12px;">{{start_time}} to {{end_time}}</p>

				<a href="{{link}}" class="button">Join Meeting</a>
				<p>Meeting Link : <span style="color: #1fa0db">{{link}}</span></p>

				<a href="http://www.google.com/calendar/event?action=TEMPLATE&text={{sub}}&dates={{c_start_time}}/{{c_end_time}}&details={{text}}&location={{link}}"
					class="atc_button">
					Add to calender
					<svg class="callogo" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
							d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>

			<p>For any queries regarding interviews or schedule please revert back.</p>
			<br>
			<br>

			Regards,<br>
			InterviewDeck.


		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>